REPLACE INTO posts VALUES(874,replace('![the weekly - curated posts from the scuttleverse](&Q9wEqKM6UtKmMpI+W17MuwTSNTQpEtSnLvTFrgVI5EE=.sha256)\n\n# Recent Days in Scuttlebutt\n\n## Totally Random\n\n[@Beni Grind](@i/gfWqlqxBq9JkYhWIT0whiczxDTySFr9KXVwZgVavw=.ed25519) [went for a ride](%GWhhx0Ixb5dZJtTnWnEUxaMtd9MYZemO8CDxrPbFCbA=.sha256) and shared a lovely picture. \n\n![a unicycle leaned against a tree beside a beautiful ocean inlet between mountains.](&G3/LW8wrlJlrVR5Pt/P0VnnUUG2Jx+2hnDvvKdJdvt0=.sha256)\n\n\n----\n[@dangerousbeans](@TXKFQehlyoSn8UJAIVP/k2BjFINC591MlBC2e2d24mA=.ed25519)\n[swam with ice](%VUT8xw29RhQWT3n8kL+WvnixMFOiNbynJrYBnX9p83w=.sha256)\n\n![dangerousbeans hols a chunk of ice while squatting in very cold water](&dt4ADUkit7mDEK9JY1dDmf8VU3HP6sUq+wlKyDdhEVs=.sha256)\n\n----\n\n[@gmarcos87](@RmClT86x/o66QdW1dqAfj5Jek4qxUf8rtmvAlhZeZFg=.ed25519) went for [an aftenoon walk on the lake](%EcFpsRDsDKxL/IHdvtEnIJckXjBEUIrb/SAMyVGYHpY=.sha256).\n\n![a woman and child stand beside a lake surrounded by lush green foliage and water plants](&GREzcgXjpVto04+JWy92+O7eSMlBDdhRIz67oq5pR0w=.sha256)\n\nThey also shared [a visual story](%K7nD5sP5fGqk2aHX8Pna1tpXdofMcDUOjCE4pLvRFEA=.sha256) about the "entangled forest" they live in at this time of the year. \n\n![a thick vine grows around a small tree](&Go4IZP+hlRJxZi5U3APoWMp6bmghU49ajPYXkLuRylI=.sha256)\n\n---- \n[@SoapDog (SPX)](@0xkjAty6RSr5uhbAvi0rbVR2g9Bz+89qiKth48ECQBE=.ed25519) shared more London spots for tasty coffee and tea. I thought I''d enjoy sitting for a spell in [this one](%JysAwNGwypXODgQnOtfYv600aVLVcHYPN4MOYbeJo+g=.sha256). Then I saw the nice tea set and understood why. \n\n![House of Morocco in London](&Z+Km7cnlPyA4HbcFzpzK0Bf5C1EM/h6873HKizMXrSo=.sha256)\n\n\n----\n[@Kaotisk Hund [phone]](@n0d6cRhB9TFy7gLhzVxy9/vH6/EuUWlpG33fGox9jCo=.ed25519) shared what may be [the first sighting of a dog-giraffe hybrid](%n2wXBFtFd2kHm9K9ipWfsxgiRSdy3d9xfJLKBuehcP0=.sha256). \n\n![](&fG4rvhye/42Qy5TT5M2Es9q0AAfKakF1xMMLcqScYBM=.sha256)\n\n\n----\n[@enkiv2](@Q6jeOaoJOdFq8/3oFaOYC6bKhaVCD3IIdpjG+7Fab2M=.ed25519) says \n\n> If youre feeling unmotivated or your writing feels stale, it may be time to change up the way you write. The following is a selection of techniques you may not have tried. They can be used as exercises to get your juices flowing, or they might become your new M. O.\n\n[Check out their thread to see those techniques](%rGGASQQ+AKOBxSbRNv68nr1IenqlbqWWaNvWs6Odgb8=.sha256)\n\n----\n[@emile](@2YVYXQclEJHVzCON5dsLRwf65b2S6HnvxpGS8/LwjwY=.ed25519) shared [an nice strategy for naming channels](%erXxBXL3JZFUgG6bjnADuPtS2redeSI1RLCl6EErzLA=.sha256) in your ham radio. They''re talking specifically about Kenwood radios, but I suspect there are other radios with similar behavior.\n\n----\n[@gmarcos87](@RmClT86x/o66QdW1dqAfj5Jek4qxUf8rtmvAlhZeZFg=.ed25519) has come into possession of [a beautiful old letterpress](%9xQWDARuRkDqu3yqP9DqYtkM/Ek+hF8hrJTLjKpl4l8=.sha256) that needs some tender loving care.\n\n![part of an old letterpress on its side with weeds growing nearby](&0xrtOGvhOnk+cx3AlrMylRKAkmQEGi9SBgRxzOrljWg=.sha256)\n\n\npost 1 of 4\n','\n',char(10)));
