REPLACE INTO posts VALUES(908,replace('![the weekly - curated posts from the scuttleverse](&Q9wEqKM6UtKmMpI+W17MuwTSNTQpEtSnLvTFrgVI5EE=.sha256)\n\n# Recent Days in Scuttlebutt\n\n## Totally Random\n[@Les Orchard (mandelbrot2 desktop)](@WJkWT1k8aYbWdL5W15EAQ/i5a8AlBbFwdCWt1BqMtV0=.ed25519) [shared some cats](%cyY/uG8OIPDW0GA5KO9ChprUGydvvjIPB3fbLLb4Y70=.sha256).\n\n![two tan and white cats curled up next to each other](&PoIJxf610z74gt+VjpdNZDfkCSU+aAnBNfd2TbX0Qhc=.sha256)\n\n----\n[@Christian Bundy](@+oaWWDs8g73EZFUMfW37R/ULtFEjwKN/DczvdYihjbU=.ed25519)\n[shared another](%INobPtsPM+E7TYT6KAKZ0lJE1UtjXmhsfeeYc1bbsLM=.sha256).\n\n![Photo of Jerome the cat curled up with his paw tucked under his face and his body tucked under a fuzzy blanket.](&lIpmd0LDOouM3q8wZ2Cty3HdVQguxon2JYFAv+clFy8=.sha256)\n\n----\n[@Rabble](@THUzexG1y6kWofwiN8Lix/jNH/P6roYdlCDgpAn2HSc=.ed25519) shared [a sunset in Portland Oregon, USA](%7NucrEf4nC0RDgMuSncvhHdod8lrbXfJZMvpMmBDcEM=.sha256).\n\n![a red sunset with silhouetted trees in Portland Oregon USA](&swyFisWysCwzK2uuQQm8RTtgoskswZtETb8nCKefnhQ=.sha256)\n\n\n\n----\n[@Fbio Emilio Costa  (Patchwork-Requeriment Room)](@UaDd69LROKdpgNokDjdyxgxmXH0J/HD1eK7KEb98/+g=.ed25519) shared [some photos from the Chinese New Year celebration in So Paulo](%jUIgPfZGdoct/dmNc16a9yCcBU72W5h4Pm/iEn8nmFc=.sha256). \n\n![Ano_Novo_Chins_2020(20200201)0125_thumb.jpg](&drjcg+x7CDf/VAq/KAFh7BUK60fUtHqfwfGQhIpFvIw=.sha256)\n\n![Ano_Novo_Chins_2020(20200201)0215_thumb.jpg](&mSGOcb+/aQpNtrVNOOIXVAODizjy0ddLuAlYGm9hjpw=.sha256)\n\n\n\n----\n\n[@skyebend](@F/Lw6U9khCl8f/BrfYbSnsd1jMFqK+9otnyKBwfp9Es=.ed25519) writes about "...certain [trivial features of daily office life](%rLivI9UIjm+l3Ud+az5EXfhwGXp+QB95NxDO/xtyEdQ=.sha256) that can be observed to sniff out organizational dysfunction."\n\n## Solarpunk\n\n[@Isabela](@Xe+wuSGAaEdwgyI/ql2WVgPG64Mqf8tVHU0VXne9Ki8=.ed25519) posted about the hardware for [the water management prototype](%+4S9NgeS9dSWB01HIgEVHRJALp6nM14Vk7h6zZZjjUc=.sha256) they''re working on in Moinho. (The post is in Portugese and English)\n\n![sistema gerenciamento de agua.png](&YqKoZT7QxjvX99soaK2qW38T15sdkGWb6VJrlcgrAoA=.sha256)\n\n\n## Community\n[@Gergely Polonkai](@I1JSeKes1DIBawiMok7WZ8w3Auo7CTq/VMRYId22+5A=.ed25519) shared [a personal story of their family''s celebration ](%iGFhRxE+sMtvwvfedXE8sil6n6I81N2HVg8HeJqNLT0=.sha256) of a recent religious holiday. \n\n![Photo of a doll made of a sock. Its hair is made of reddish brown yarn. Its eyes and mouth are drawn with felt pen.](&CLOa5ItJ3Ds5HGnL47a3XkuOncVEPOrMhPVgHP+Tspg=.sha256)\n\npost 1 of 3\n','\n',char(10)));
