REPLACE INTO posts VALUES(974,replace('![the weekly - curated posts from the scuttleverse](&Q9wEqKM6UtKmMpI+W17MuwTSNTQpEtSnLvTFrgVI5EE=.sha256)\n\n# Recent Days in Scuttlebutt\n\n## Totally Random\n[@Blackbeard](@XjqVy9IZqxbFYJ46fl5a9cqa1Grsf8yd6i/hIv+pcN0=.ed25519) said "[Hello](%uXr7ypnZSHpSa7lR8GaFbNRSjOfTugmLG/jVhdZZW58=.sha256)" with a Palm Tree.\n\n![a palm tree silhouetted against the sunset](&p7ixJKTZY3LFI400I8yVk402FAp5deN//LhskTvSXlQ=.sha256)\n\n----\n[@emile](@2YVYXQclEJHVzCON5dsLRwf65b2S6HnvxpGS8/LwjwY=.ed25519) shared [a flower](%+0nHM7qoH3wGm4bb6G7H0Q3Hs0Rr314Z7ORbgmzxqAs=.sha256).\n\n![a flower in front of a window that overlooks snowy ground](&ES5OR4CStrUYiQzXp4Cy/92uzgB/LY5TcJP3JgWarRI=.sha256)\n\n\n----\n![Fbio Emilio Costa](&Iklun9PeasoP9J8cJonlq2iXQB6HqekSoXGRFRydThg=.sha256) shared [an urban sunrise](%QaothvHv0dPaDVsZ+QnooWn4x9UYgCz3N8V4nTRdJtA=.sha256) and a self portrait.\n\n![urban sunrise](&Iklun9PeasoP9J8cJonlq2iXQB6HqekSoXGRFRydThg=.sha256)\n\n\n----\n[@dangerousbeans](@TXKFQehlyoSn8UJAIVP/k2BjFINC591MlBC2e2d24mA=.ed25519) shared [a moment of peace](%cKxfk5Hk5sS8ZBNEYL0yzsUIdD/SQ+lEkR8RXZnGjPE=.sha256) that I desperately envy.\n\n![hammock coffee](&LwclJwWGgDCaeLb53XpwTOknXYuerBezJYS/IfM7ubw=.sha256)\n\n\n----\n[@Horacio](@L1JoMwhZLXETW9zIf98c7Q22/ZUJUX09ZJJViUwLlOY=.ed25519) shared "[4 Laws of behavior change](%SptrHoYu+tFTKyNPiZ8ZtNDyOQusDbduOrTXEsZ311E=.sha256)" that can help change your behavior, or get others to adopt a behavior you desire.\n\n\n## Solarpunk\n\n[@A-pantz](@L3nSIvWsEuUawfmfvwP/XmlB93E8tmdpw7OagUyENq8=.ed25519) shared [the creation of a Bamboo Shade House](%tbG5lwdUqUtWQL5EhUdwtlhrj4dG0oSfHRZri3z+2E8=.sha256).\n\n![footing-composite from rusty brake rotors for a bamboo shade house](&0bwKCIKt+mORRi71zzPiLprTC9HyFRQNmhxyeCKIbgY=.sha256)\n\n\n\n\n## Software\nThere have a been at least three Patchwork releases this week fixing various bugs and regressions. If you use it, be sure to [grab the latest version](https://github.com/ssbc/patchwork/releases/).\n\n-----\n[@Powersource](@Vz6v3xKpzViiTM/GAe+hKkACZSqrErQQZgv4iqQxEn8=.ed25519)\n\n"managed to publish [the] SSB Webextension demo (repo) as a firefox addon." Details in [the thread](%/GzxwrxBAeh0rcFXK5ihv/F/+GhXa2gqHXrhUQYJ7Nw=.sha256).\n\n![ssb browser demo as web extension screenshot](&WkDKe2vARRqz4SiYB7AHDcnIUPHJEcP/YF6VoHl4SiA=.sha256)\n\n----\n[@cel](@f/6sQ6d2CMxRUhLpspgGIulDxDCwYD7DzFzPNr7u5AU=.ed25519) shared ssb-exec. A "...[script to show who is following you that you have not followed back](%M0oKQswfj5xUFYgcftZxSxFv2sBILEv3IHEsEs1s1q8=.sha256), filtered/sorted by recency..., length of their feed, and age..."\n\n![ssb-exec-followers screenshot](&Mc0B1DJnhxAww+1YJ8jfnvOtKbdQkm5MDlSJxr8fVpM=.sha256 screenshot of followers.js running in Dillo, with names blurred and numbers fuzzed)\n\nRequires some geekery to use. \n\n-----\n\npost 1 of 2\n','\n',char(10)));
REPLACE INTO posts VALUES(984,replace('[@cinnamon](@fBS90Djngwl/SlCh/20G7piSC064Qz2hBBxbfnbyM+Y=.ed25519) released [Buntimer](%6Kk4ezDdOlO6+F7V0Rp8iAIjlupzxbEyrPdZ2MnajRs=.sha256) \n\n> I have trouble doing things on time. Ill get deeply engrossed in projects and forget to eat or take medicine. So, I built a little timer app to help myself. Maybe its useful to you too.\n\n![buntimer screenshot](&gxLMJoc2AowrLLnXFnvU51V9tyzaR5JgS1RIjTqhy1E=.sha256)\n\n\nLater in the thread SoapDog took it and made it into a Firefox Extension.\n\n----\nI talked about [Software That Lasts](%Gc9o9vg7FlPPeC3x7K5HbGz4BLlE+qr/R20s32OM55M=.sha256); the problem with the recent trend towards cloud-based software, and some thoughts for your future software choices.\n\n> When your data only exists in software that you dont host yourself it is no longer yours. It can disappear at any moment. Your datas future is dependent upon a companys continued profits and interests.\n\n\n## Geeky\n[@mixmix](@ye+QM09iPcDJD6YvQYjoQc7sLF/IFhmNbEqgdzQo3lQ=.ed25519) "...[improved the at-mentions suggestions algorithm of [the ssb-suggest library]](%YkZcQeOTxmVjNtYgR6dEdS2nGMCheEOCpPYr2Em8iso=.sha256)" and added it to the master branch of Patchbay.\n\n![ssb suggest screenshot in patchbay](&0WJUjnwY++YjCxrDZIlEnP0FFmVinnUIUgk7EZOFHAg=.sha256)\n\n\n\n------------\n### Summary Data\n\nThis weeks summary was curated from ~466 threads by ~153 authors by [@masukomi](@LzTjF5eAVC6xprPMGeNzqEP/EEBIGpM6hDaaY10hrz8=.ed25519), **with the support of my lovely patrons**. If you''d like to help continue this creation you can [become a patron on Patreon](https://www.patreon.com/the_weekly).\n\n\n\npost 2 of 2\n','\n',char(10)));
REPLACE INTO posts VALUES(990,replace('![the weekly - curated posts from the scuttleverse](&Q9wEqKM6UtKmMpI+W17MuwTSNTQpEtSnLvTFrgVI5EE=.sha256)\n\n# Recent Days in Scuttlebutt\n\n## Totally Random\n[@Beni Grind](@i/gfWqlqxBq9JkYhWIT0whiczxDTySFr9KXVwZgVavw=.ed25519) gave us [another beautiful picture](%FNsyRVoAhY3qcd1pNUutSetwg8vhUBUSlM6aNVF3XjI=.sha256) powered by their unicycle. \n\n![a unicycle leans against a stone wall on a dirt road through green fields. a sun sets behind jagged mountains in the distance.](&Q6RXjmzHFuar62TODCij8giIHcHVh2sRfEuaq91WAgg=.sha256)\n\nThey then [did a thing](%rKPFvZ0/f31+O2gFBI0Jj9d8SfIPV+ZxY8XjxWNxF3I=.sha256) which I suspect had no unicycle involvement.\n\n![a large cabin with wood protecting its windows sits high up in snow covered mountains. There are no tracks through the fresh snow around it.](&y9hvt/3t+EteWAb1CwzA0kVnXQwSv9uyo8iHno1rL2s=.sha256)\n\n\n----\n\n[@dangerousbeans](@TXKFQehlyoSn8UJAIVP/k2BjFINC591MlBC2e2d24mA=.ed25519) is [growing basil on a boat](%uY1dV8RUf8ugpVNPMMUET8PCiZXPC5yF1R+EeYH6Azc=.sha256). \n\n![basil](&o9cF9mxTeuzy7MT/TvqLENjX79BOIA2XlUua1weKAFQ=.sha256)\n\n\n----\n[@SoapDog](@gaQw6z30GpfsW9k8V5ED4pHrg8zmrqku24zTSAINhRg=.ed25519) [crossed the Rhine](%4vUHmh82AHoNJn/tipNAqcl79AEMf/WOiT7jkblG2Jc=.sha256) and shared some pictures.\n\n![a statue overlooks a river with shield, spear, and cloak set down behind them](&/hqQ2MLzppqQCpoe5iLojCjMVtB5C1W6Hvdk1u++9Iw=.sha256)\n\n----\n[@sean](@N/vWpVVdD1e8IbACUQE4EVGL6+aodQfbQZ8ByC+k79s=.ed25519) is [tapping maple trees](%gBplGJrTMC2xv8oDEMMYTazHjiX0bvzgkSkEXvOIgPA=.sha256).\n\n![a maple tree drips clear sap into a jar](&wEZYyxNs0mWabqnosOVM1HqTr73Z/vuxzCFBOedqYhw=.sha256)\n\n\n----\n[@masukomi](@LzTjF5eAVC6xprPMGeNzqEP/EEBIGpM6hDaaY10hrz8=.ed25519) (me) wrote far too many words [Comparing D&D with The Fantasy Trip](%0YZij1JPVoN6+DX5bXB/RVe8T5MyG9T0kNR5B29kItY=.sha256) (an old-school RPG from the 80s that just got re-released).\n\n----\n[@adz](@3u2quSQ8qX1fTx4HQKthYPDavQI4Wm88kThExFXemYo=.ed25519) [released an album](%SXlBoWd+/gO1lQvw74fxEazWDQY+cmqLOaWBVmI9BpY=.sha256)\n\n![adz''s music recording setup](&meYP6JFJpfhvWykc3uoAcAuhpQBgctPziZB7btki1SA=.sha256)\n\nand some software that''s somehow related to the making of it.\n\n![screenshot of kubismus](&7Bon8J/fuRCCcx68qNRTzDooKCclLV8C+K8owAsHrsg=.sha256)\n\n----\n[@xj9](@xuq5ATR6hDNt6/0q1RB+L1f0dyeVk1kG1JAXu4jo/GU=.ed25519) taught us how to make Red Curry Paste.\n\n![red curry paste in dry form](&WK5PbJ26VgyIvYVnQh8Jp3bpTJg8RM/cy5w1Gg3729U=.sha256)\n\n----\n[@dangerousbeans](@TXKFQehlyoSn8UJAIVP/k2BjFINC591MlBC2e2d24mA=.ed25519) was [given a boat for their boat](%K9XafowLIkZalhagsL1gR7HuNgvyMGiNFDBhh05BAAs=.sha256) by the ocean.\n\n![kayak gift of the sea](&aIIrCnjP/2fUac/EE9ol0BN09r4KPw1BJ+qwjvghyT0=.sha256)\n\n\n## Community\n[@cft](@AiBJDta+4boyh2USNGwIagH/wKjeruTcDX2Aj1r/haM=.ed25519) shared a picture of [SSB folks in Basel](%LhJZpvqMaaORd7E1S3azBPtJBSJRSFdoeXQfVSixJmA=.sha256)\n\n![SSB folks gathered together for a group photo in Basel](&9s5SJTisjcmDW0q5bAnJtDhXhgB/xIiR2XSXHLyWnik=.sha256)\n\npost 1 of 3\n','\n',char(10)));
