REPLACE INTO posts VALUES(341,replace('I didn''t take any photos, but last night we broke down and got takeout. We parked up on Grizzly Peak and had a picnic in the back of the truck. I know that me not being able to go out to dinner or picnic outside my own vehicle is like the least worst part of this pandemic but it is starting to get to me. \n\nI was genuinely impressed with [Funky Elephant''s](https://www.funkyelephantthai.com/) protocol. They have a sheet of plastic over their door, which is also locked. Order online, wave when you arrive. They open the door but you can''t breath on each other because of the plastic (plus everyone has masks on at this point). Tell them your name, they go get the order and set it on a chair just outside the door. Zero contact. Very good food, too, though thin on the vegetarian options. ','\n',char(10)));
